with some or all of the book.

00:01:15.410 --> 00:01:16.740
It's really just to give you a framework

00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:18.760
because I think the book at least raises

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:20.576
an interesting conversation
and it gives us

00:01:20.576 --> 00:01:23.290
a lot of I would say
fodder for interesting

00:01:23.290 --> 00:01:24.980
analysis and critical thinking.

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:26.790
And that's really what I
want you to walk away with.

00:01:26.790 --> 00:01:28.210
How do you think about these things?

00:01:28.210 --> 00:01:31.100
And you just need to
make your own judgment.

00:01:31.100 --> 00:01:33.230
So what I wanna do here is at least show

